title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: 4X GTA$ and RP on Open Wheel Races
content: High speeds, outlandish production budgets, corporate sponsors, interpersonal drama — it’s hard to compete with the spectacle of Open Wheel Races. The circuit also promises an eye-popping 4X GTA$ and RP on the seven fan-favorite tracks returning to the Featured Series this week. Head over to Legion Square to compete.
